items.name: CDTM Mobile Comics 条漫
items.description:
这是一个条漫模型，所以他更适用于 512*1024 和以上分辨率。

他典型的作用是：

设计出好看的漫画分镜样式。

模型中使用了50张条漫，混了一些插画风格。

如果要关闭这些风格，你需要对lora进行分层控制。

我在使用时，分层参数为：

<lora:cdtm:0.8:1,1,1,0.6,0.6,1,0.8,0.2,0,0,0,0.2,0.5,0,0,0,0>

注意：

10层目前0.2，11层目前0.5，这两层似乎会影响对话框的保留数量。

可以酌情增加或进一步减少。

关于交流，目前还没有主页。

有在动漫这一块研究的朋友，可以加WX：s-binghao

日本語の紹介：

これは拡散モデルなので、512*1024以上の解像度に適しています。

彼の典型的な役割は、

美しい漫画の絵コンテをデザインします。

モデルには50枚の漫画が使用されており、いくつかのイラストスタイルが混在しています。

これらのスタイルをオフにするには、loraを階層的に制御する必要があります。

使用中の階層パラメータは次のとおりです。

<lora:cdtm:0.8:1,1,1,0.6,0.6,1,0.8,0.2,0,0,0,0.2,0.5,0,0,0,0>

注：

10層は現在0.2、11層は現在0.5で、この2層はダイアログボックスの予約数に影響を与えるようです。

適宜増やしたり、さらに減らしたりすることができます。

コミュニケーションについては、まだホームページがありません。

アニメという研究をしている友人がいて、WX：s-binghaoを加えることができます

items.name: Princess Amira, Egyptian Aisha - Neopets
items.description:
Version 5:

Version 5 epoch 8

This version was trained less, which means that there is a lower chance that the resulting image gets deep fried. But it also means the character becomes more human and less Aisha.

I also added the antennae tag in the training data, so the antennae (Aisha's extra ears) is removable if it is put in the negative prompt.

The outfits are also more adjustable, the previous version sometimes forces Amira to wear her default outfit.

For some reason she has an animal nose now, I tagged it in the training dataset but putting animal nose in negative prompt doesn't seem to do much.

Version 2:

The previous version had problems with giving random blue faces and very thick outlines.

I think it was because of the tagging, there were a couple of images with a blue dog as a pet that wasn't tagged. This version fixes that. I also added 14 more images which were good generations from the previous version with some touchups to remove the errors. So this version was trained on 34 images instead of just 21 in version 1.

10 repeats, 18th epoch was selected.

Version 1:

Not too sure about this one because I only got 21 images to train from and some are really low resolution. Because if that I did 15 repeats, so in 20 epochs there were 3000+ steps.

If there are enough good images generated from this version (with different poses and backgrounds) I will be willing to make a version 2.

Epoch 12 and 14 gave good results depending on the base model used, in the end I picked 14 even though there are some serious errors for some models, though working on the prompt might also circumvent this.

items.name: Amnero - Kyouka Jinrui Amunero | Character Lora
items.description:
V2.0

This update makes the model a whole lot more flexible by training on NAI with small training steps.

Use a weight of 0.7-1. Check the XYZ plot for more details.

The model details contains 2 helpful prompt collection for getting the usual hairstyle and clothing respectively.

Unlike v1.0 this model works very well with other style LoRA. To get depictions closer to the original I recommend combining this with my Hyocorou Style LoRA at 0.5 weight.

V1.0

A character model trained for AOM3 using the collab/guide by holostrawberry [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free - colabs | Stable Diffusion Other | Civitai

This model is nsfw and has a bias towards topless depictions.

Check out the character at 419681

I recommend using a weight of 0.85-1.

As this is a hyocorou original character with no fanart this lora also affects the artstyle. To combine the model with other styles a weight around 0.85 works best (I have included quite a few examples). At 0.6 and below there is little resemblance as can be seen in the XYZ plot.

For the classic outfit use these or similar prompts:

side braid, headband, hair ornament, (highleg panties, highleg, shorts,thighhighs:1.2), off-shoulder jacket, oversized jacket, bare shoulders, tube top, red ribbon, hair ribbon, puffy sleeves

For the alternate hairstyle twintails works more often than not.

Please leave a review if you enjoyed this Lora or have problems with it. I'd also be interested in how the lora behaves with other base checkpoints so why don't you give it a try and throw some images down below!

items.description:
I asked a friend of mine hey which armor should i do next and I expected some popular ones and then he said what about Anjanath and i thought okay i like the design but what about the dataset....

I searched for an extend amount time and i only found 16 Images that I could use and from these 16 I wouldnt have used half of them if i had a choice.

No activation token just prompt it all pictures contain anjanath (armor) that might help. Also because of the scarcity of images random monster might appear in the background.

So the Locon works good I guess im not entirely happy with its performance I trained it on higher Alpha and Dim settings because of the lack of pictures if you combine it with other lora/Lycoris some pieces of the armor might not work properly (the helmet in particular).
I wouldnt recommend using it on more than 0.9 or 0.8 it also depends on some factors like:" Are you using it together with another locon/lora ?"

I will upload all the epochs that I deem usable just test them out and take the one you like best I will include pictures from all of them in the preview

Also I was lazy with the preview picture prompts

Have fun generating.

items.name: Madi Collins
items.description:
‼ IMPORTANT ‼

  • Your voice matters! Show your support and leave a post, comment and most importantly a review! ⭐

  • Custom LORAs available upon request. Just buymeacoffee.☕

  • (workflow advice below) 👇

📝Biography📝

🌟Madi Collins🌟

also known as Mady Collins but born as Mandi Collins, is an American actress and model, born on May 7, 1998, in Chicago, Illinois. She stands at 4 feet 10 inches (147 cm) tall and weighs 94 pounds (43 kg), with a slender figure measuring 32A-22-33. Madi is of Caucasian descent and has striking green eyes and red hair. Her body measurements are 32A-24-33, and she has tattoos on her right forearm, inside right forearm, under right forearm, and "La vie est belle" on her left thigh. Madi's distinctive features include her attractive figure and confidence.

Madi Collins began her career in the entertainment industry in 2020. She has since worked with various studios, primarily in videos and web scenes. Madi has also performed in videos alongside various well-known actresses in the entertainment industry.

Madi is a self-proclaimed dog lover and enjoys traveling, shopping, taking selfies, and surfing the internet as hobbies. She has gained immense popularity on social media, with a large following that admires her captivating personality, beauty, and endearing smile. She has primarily earned her wealth through her acting career, with an estimated net worth of $1 to $2 million. Currently, Madi is still active in the entertainment industry and continues to work on various projects while making content for her Only Fans and Model Hub profiles.

💡Workflow Advice💡

🔧Prompt and Sampling🔧

  • Most images have been generated with LORA weighted @ .75 - 1.

  • For photoreal shots, I've found sampling steps best well above 50 give better results.

  • ControlNet is your friend. Embrace the dark side.😈

    • Tile presample and model is good for extreme close ups

    • I use segmentation for lots of my generations now (not so much when I generated samples for Madi but maybe on a version update)

🚀Upscaling🚀

  • Try the Ultimate SD upscale script!

  • Sometimes I just send it to Ultimate SD upscale after a quick render and run 2x at a scale of two.

  • Ultimate SD upscale script used @ ~.15 - .4 denoising using 8x NMKD Faces or 4X UltraSharp redraw upscalers.

🗒️Side Notes🗒️

  • Help me help you: Leave a review if you've used this LORA.

  • Most of my gens are not voodoo or outside of workflows I've indicated here or in my other posts.

    • In other words: Leave a comment if you are having issues getting good output, I'll try to respond with suggestions.

items.name: 【CHECKPOINT】 MAKIMAKII
items.description:
2023/9/3 update

・Ver2 リリース

　楽しんで！

2023/5/28 update

・このモデルは作者の意向で量産型にしたくありません。

　500DLを上限として、以降はこのページのチェックポイントファイルが削除されます。

2023/5/24 update

・シャープなイラストのニーズに対応するため既存LoRaのテストを行いました。

　Sharpness Tweaker LoRA　でシャープになる事を確認しています。

　他の対応策もHPで検証結果を含めて記載しています。

2023/5/23 update

・私のHPで概要を記載しました。Civitaiよりも少し詳しく記載しています。。

　また、今後サポートは私のHPで実施いたします。（将来に渡って無料です。）

https://www.makima.site/stable-diffusion/makimakii/

2023/5/22 update

・モデル変更はありませんが重要な事が判明したので記載

①BREAK構文で区切る事でシャープになり発色が良くなることが分かりました。

　[品質],BREAK,[背景],BREAK,[女の子]　など

　モデル自体の不具合ではなく、Counterfeltのように少し癖のある呪文が必要です。

②裏を返せば、BREAK構文を使わない場合はソフトに描き、BREAK構文を使えばくっきりシャープなイラストを描けます。

この点が分かったので、下記に記載している問題点は解消とさせていただきます。

③サンプリング回数は23回以上を推奨とさせて頂きます。かなり少ない方なので効率的に作画ができると思います。

④こちらは元々記載していた内容ですが、単語の羅列でも描画はしますが推奨はセンテンスを記載する事です。具体的に記載するほど描画精度はあがります。

⑤品質呪文を調整する事で少し崩れた綺麗なアニメ風イラストも描けます。

BREAK構文が入っているサンプルを保存したので記載方法はサンプルの呪文をご確認ください。

2023/5/21 update

このモデルは女の子を線画を細く描きながら、表情を柔らかく、背景はシャープネスが残るような少しアニメに寄った感じの描画する事を目的に作成しました。

このモデルは高精細というよりは、味のあるイラストになる事を目指しています。

優しい表情の女の子が多く描画されます。背景のみでも機能します。

初心者の方が直ぐに描きやすいようにVAEは焼き込んでいます。

特徴：

・女の子をソフトに描きます。

・人間の肌色をなるべく再現できるように頑張っています。

（黒くなり過ぎないようにしています。）

・女の子を柔らかく描写する目的がありソフトフォーカス寄りのイラストになります。

　※シャープに描きたい時は、呪文でContrastやSharpnessを唱えてあげると良くなる場合があります。（強度はイラストによって異なります。当然、効かない場合もあります。）

BREAK構文を記載する方が確実なので訂正します。

・背景は基本的にしっかりと描きます。

・エフェクトや洋服は種類多く、背景なども種類が多いと思います。

・VAEについてはチェックポイントに焼き込んであります。

（vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors）

　色が濃くなりすぎる時はVAEを自動設定にしてください。薄いと感じる場合はお好みのVAEを設定ください。

呪文の記載方法：

基本的に単語でも描画しますが、うまくいかない時はセンテンスで記載する事を推奨しています。

補足：

今後も適時バージョンアップを行う予定です。

ディテールがパキって出る素晴らしいモデルは既に多数存在しているので、私は女の子をソフトに描くモデルを作り続けるでしょう。

ファイルの種類：

MAKIMAKI_V1.safetensors：フルバージョンです

MAKIMAKI_light_V1.safetensors：軽量化版です

サンプル画像：

・アップスケーラを通すと高精細なのが描けます。

・個人的にお勧めはControlnetのShuffulとSoftedge_hedです。

問題点：

・ファイルが重いです。ごめんなさいデータ詰め込んだらこうなりました。

　→　ファイルは重いですが、多くのファイルがあるため多種多様な描写ができます。

　　　ここは今後も修正予定はありません。

　　　１０GBを超えないようにコントロールはしたいと考えています。

・ワイドビューの時に女の子の顔が崩れやすいですが、絵柄としてはアーティスティックな作品になる事が多いです。

　→　解消済（5/22Update内容をご参照ください）

Fast Negative Embedding

Do you like what I do? Consider supporting me on Patreon 🅿️ or feel free to buy me a coffee ☕

Token mix of my usual negative embedding. This way it's faster to use and easier to reproduce.

I'm also working on a much stronger one that doesn't preserve styles but it's good on base models without style loras applied. I plan to upload it during the next week, so be sure to leave a ❤️ to be notified of future updates.

This is very much a work in progress, but since I'm already using it in examples, I thought I should upload it.

Additionally, if you find this too overpowering, use it with weight, like (FastNegativeEmbedding:0.9).

Update: added FastNegativeV2. It shouldn't be necessary to lower the weight.

Of course, don't use this in the positive prompt.
This includes Nerf's Negative Hand embedding.

items.name: ComfyUI Manager
items.description:
This extension provides assistance in installing and managing custom nodes for ComfyUI.

Announcement:

  • Versions prior to V0.22.2 will no longer detect missing nodes unless using a local database. Please update ComfyUI-Manager to the latest version.

  • Update ComfyUI to latest version (Aug 4)

Features:

  • missing nodes: automatic recognition and suggest installation

  • custom nodes: install/uninstall/update/enable/disable

    • Node suggestion of A1111 alternatives.

  • ComfyUI: update

  • models: download

  • runtime preview method setup

Please refer to the GitHub page for more detailed information.

https://github.com/ltdrdata/ComfyUI-Manager

Install guide:

  • Method 1 (windows portable version):

    • Download

    • Please extract the downloaded compressed file and move the install-manager-for-portable-version.bat file to the ComfyUI_windows_portable directory where the run_nvidia_gpu.bat file is located.

    • Double click install-manager-for-portable-version.bat in explorer

    • Restart ComfyUI

  • Method 2 (general):

    • goto ComfyUI/custom_nodes in cmd

    • git clone https://github.com/ltdrdata/ComfyUI-Manager

    • Restart ComfyUI

Requirements:

  • An issue has been reported regarding malfunction when an outdated version of the Git program is installed.

  • https://git-scm.com/downloads

items.name: 崩坏：星穹铁道 - 符玄
Landscape_PhotoReal
items.description:
日本語の説明は後半にあります。

This is a merged model created to produce photorealistic background images for web conference.

I don't know why, but many photorealistic models become illustrative when creating background / landscape images without characters, so we tried various models and merged the few that could output photorealistic backgrounds.

As a byproduct, this model can produce beautiful photorealistic female characters that are a fusion of Asian and Western descent.

Actually this model is also the base model for CityEdge_FusionMix. (CityEdge_FusionMix is a 2.5D version of this model block-weighted merged with animated models.)

It is recommended to use "Easy Photorealism" for using this model for photorealisitic output.

List of my models

  • CityEdgeMix : Simple photo-realistic model based on Chilled family

  • CityEdge_ToonMix : Simple 2.5D anime-like model based on CityEdgeMix

  • CityEdge_2dToonMix : Pure 2D anime-like model merging only 2D models

  • CityEdge_StyleMix : Anime-like model with detail depiction by making use of block-merge

  • CityEdge_FusionMix : 2.5D model focusing on unique depiction through merging many models and block-merge.

  • Landscape_Photoreal : Model that produces photorealistic output, whether with characters or just the background

  • CityEdge_DollyMix : Model that produces doll-like and 3D animated movie-like output

Web会議の背景画像を作成するために作ったマージモデルです。

多くのフォトリアル系モデルは、なぜかキャラクターなしの背景画像を作るとイラスト的になってしまうため、さまざまなモデルを試し、フォトリアルな背景を出力できる数少ないモデルをマージして作成しています。

副産物として、アジア系と欧米系が絶妙に融合したフォトリアルな女性キャラクターを出力することもできるようになっています。

なお、このモデルは、CityEdge_FusionMixのベースモデルにもなっています。（CityEdge_FusionMixは、このモデルにアニメ系モデルを階層マージして2.5D化したものです）

使用にあたっては、「Easy Photorealism」の使用を推奨します。

モデル一覧

  • CityEdgeMix : Chilled系をベースにしたシンプルなフォトリアル系マージモデル

  • CityEdge_ToonMix : CityEdgeMixを2.5D化したシンプルな2.5Dアニメモデル

  • CityEdge_2dToonMix : 2Dモデルだけをマージしたピュア2Dアニメモデル

  • CityEdge_StyleMix : 階層マージを駆使してディテール描写にこだわったアニメモデル

  • CityEdge_FusionMix : 多数のモデルのマージと階層マージによる独自の描写にこだわった2.5Dモデル

  • Landscape_Photoreal : キャラクターがいても、背景だけでも、フォトリアルな出力が得られるモデル

  • CityEdge_DollyMix : ドール調・3Dアニメ映画調の出力が得られるモデル

items.name: ProPortrait
items.description:
Built with the concept “Prompt less, Post more”

Just only short prompt and you will get a realistic portrait photo. Let you focus on posting on social media, building engagement, and doing other things that are important to you.

*** This Model needs VAE !!! ***

Overview:

  • The purpose of this model is to generate a portrait photo.

  • These models require a VAE. You can try mse-840000-ema or anything. I have a photo of the comparison in the Comparison section (below)

    • If you got bugs, adding '--no-half-vae' to the argument will solve it.

Recommends:

  • Prompt:

    Try to start with(skindentation:1.2), (realistic:1.1), best quality, photorealistic, + your prompt (eg. 1 girl, wearing a white shirt)

    Negative: lowres, normal quality, ((monochrome)), ((grayscale)), BadHand v4

  • Steps: I recommend 30-45 (You can use higher, but many times do not have a big difference)

  • Sampling Methods: You can see the comparison in the Comparison section (below).

  • Sizes:

    Medium shot: 512x512, 512x768, 512x904

    Long shot (full body): 768x1152, 768x1356

    Can be used both vertically and horizontally

  • Hires. fix: Use Denoising strength less than 0.6 (but you can try >= 0.7, sometimes you will get problems with the hands)

Comparison:

items.name: Sword Poses Depth
items.description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

Install Instructions:

open stable diffusion -> extensions -> install from URL -> https://github.com/Mikubill/sd-webui-controlnet.git

click Apply and restart UI

Then download from https://huggingface.co/webui/ControlNet-modules-safetensors/tree/main the file control_depth-fp16.safetensor

place it inside extensions/sd-webui-controlnet/models

After all of this, you will have a ControlNet v1.1.112 just above Script in txt2image tab

Open it, place the pose (black and white image, not the example one) you want to replicate by selecting it from your computer and place it in the image selection square box. You can also drag and drop.

Select preprocessor NONE, check Enable Checkbox, select control_depth-fp16 in Model list, check Controlnet is more important in Control Mode (or leave balanced).

Then generate your image, don't forget to write a proper prompt for the image.

I uploaded the pose images and 1 example generated image with that pose using the same prompt for all of them. But you can modify the prompt to fit what you want.

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians

items.name: Billy Butcher from "The Boys"
items.description:
William J. "Billy" Butcher, or "Billy the Butcher", is a fictional character and antihero in the comic book and Amazon Prime series The Boys, created by Garth Ennis and Darick Robertson. He is the leader of The Boys, a group of CIA-sponsored vigilantes who observe, record and sometimes liquidate "Supes" (i.e. "superpowered" or "superhuman" individuals, often acting as "superheroes") artificially created by the mega-conglomerate Vought.

This model is trained with SFW sources only. If you get NSFW content, well, it's on you.

Please provide constructive criticism.

You can support me here to be able to render better models (https://ko-fi.com/djo226). Supporters can request model.

Prompt : Butcher, a man, photography, trending on artstation, sharp focus, studio photo, intricate details, highly detailed, by greg rutkowski <lora:Butcher:0.9>

Negative prompt: (deformed iris, deformed pupils, semi-realistic, cgi, 3d, render, sketch, cartoon, drawing, anime, mutated hands and fingers:1.4), (deformed, distorted, disfigured:1.3), poorly drawn, bad anatomy, wrong anatomy, extra limb, missing limb, floating limbs, disconnected limbs, mutation, mutated, ugly, disgusting, amputation

Steps: 150 (yes!), Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale: 12, Seed: -1, Face restoration: GFPGAN, Size: 768x1024, Model hash: 81086e2b3f, Model: realisticVisionV20_v20

Face restoration is optional, may provide better result if not activated.

Use Butcher as trigger.

Important:

This Lora model is a virtual representation of a natural person and it is important to emphasize that its use must not be illegal or degrading. I want to remind you that any infringement in this regard is the responsibility of the user and not that of the designer of this model.

It is crucial to respect laws and ethical standards regarding the use of this technology. Any abusive or illegal use of this model is strictly prohibited and could result in legal consequences for the user.

As the designer of this model, I take the responsibility of ensuring that it is used in an ethical and responsible manner very seriously. I rely on each user to do the same and to act in compliance with the laws and ethical standards in force.
